      "description": {
        "value": "<p>Your animal companion roars or demonstrates its prowess in a display of power that shakes enemies. Your animal companion attempts a Performance check. Compare the result to the Will DCs of each enemy creature within 20 feet of your animal companion. Regardless of the outcome, each affected creature is immune to your animal companion's Dazzling Display for 24 hours.</p><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The enemy is frightened 2.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The enemy is frightened 1.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The enemy is clumsy 1 until the end of your turn.</p>"
