        "value": "<p>Your animal companion pulls an enemy into a more advantageous position, or drags an ally to safety. Your animal companion attempts an Athletics check against the Fortitude DC of the target. If the target is willing or unconscious, treat the result as one degree higher.</p><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your animal companion can drag the target a distance up to their Speed.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> Your animal companion can drag the target a distance up to half their Speed.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> Your animal companion fails to move the target.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your animal companion fails to move the target and falls prone.</p>"
